From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 18:47:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Render & share: high-res hero photo + 360 spin GIF (feature
 #3)

A CaptureRig publishes the Design scene's renderer/scene/camera; capture.ts
renders the piece off-screen into a high-res sRGB, tone-mapped image (Photo, 2x
the on-screen size, PNG) and spins the piece a full turn capturing frames that
gifenc encodes into an animated GIF (360 GIF), with live progress on the button.
Neither disturbs what's on screen. New Export group on the Design toolbar.

Verified headless: Photo -> valid 411 KB PNG (correct gold/sRGB), 360 GIF -> valid
GIF89a; 295 tests pass, strict build clean.
